Package: shiny.plate
Title: Create a new shiny project that includes CSS and JS files.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Madsen", , "chris.madsen@gov.bc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package gives a single function (new_shiny_plate) that creates a newshiny project in the desired directory. This R project includes a CSS file and a Javascript file that are hooked into the UI. The app UI is built using {bslib}.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
